wo mni krs won nn fra,

ha bi n ma fn myta a t

When we go to the bush,

Alfa Amadu, you say that when you go to the bush, when you see the squirrel, you tell your dog: "catch it, catch it!". The dog runs with zeal it follows it till the squirrel till the squirrel enters into the whole

ka a si nn b-la tgun, a mn b w l , a saa bri, wl naa gbn, a naa bta

si wl ngnden, a saa gbn a naa bta

, i btaa f yan nt, i k i la wln mni bla, kln gb l, an mn anu bri kln si yl lg l,

ma fo i dn-na wo le ma, ka

bi tgun, n mn wli, n mnaa kli, a si na, a mni n yn kamin woo a si a f la-frifri, a ni na n ma.

i bi i la wl k, s mni ko, a i dn-na b l le, a naa la, ka a i ki-la i la l ma le, a nii la l kntan?

s mn ko, mn yaa k-la a drinden n de l..
when the night come, the thing that makes him accustomed to me,

kyi sba le, an b-ta, an i ta-la wyas l

d tgun, an k.. an k kl ble
the othere one.. they said there was now straw
